<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Flyobo Travel</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 32px;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa, #ffffff);
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4B0082, #00b4d8);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 36px 30px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .quote-box {
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f9fbff;
      border-left: 5px solid #4B0082;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background: #4B0082;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.35);
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
      .content { padding: 24px 20px; }
      .cta-btn { padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 15px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to <span style="color: #FFD700;">Flyobo Travel</span></h1>
      <p>"Jobs fill your pocket, but adventures fill your soul." ‚Äì Jaime Lyn Beatty</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

      <p>We're absolutely thrilled to welcome you to <strong>Flyobo Travel</strong> ‚Äî your gateway to extraordinary adventures and unforgettable experiences! üåç‚úàÔ∏è</p>

      <p>Here's what's waiting for you as a member:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>‚úÖ Access to exclusive travel packages and deals</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Personalized travel recommendations</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Real-time booking and trip management</li>
        <li>‚úÖ 24/7 customer support and travel assistance</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Member-only discounts and special offers</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="quote-box">
        "Not all those who wander are lost." ‚Äì J.R.R. Tolkien
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="https://flyobo.com" class="cta-btn">Explore Your Dashboard</a>
      </div>

      <p>Let's turn dreams into destinations and transform miles into moments. Your next adventure awaits!</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 36px;">With wanderlust and excitement,<br/>
      <strong>The Flyobo Travel Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Flyobo Travel. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>"Flyobo: Fly Off, Break Out"</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
